# 💰 Budget Tracker API

Django REST Framework yordamida qurilgan professional darajadagi shaxsiy moliya boshqaruv tizimi.

---

## 🚀 Texnologiyalar

| Texnologiya | Versiya |
|---|---|
| Python | 3.12 |
| Django | 6.0+ |
| Django REST Framework | 3.14+ |
| PostgreSQL | 15+ |
| JWT (SimpleJWT) | — |
| drf-spectacular (Swagger) | — |
| django-filter | — |
| python-environs | — |
| requests | — |
| python-dateutil | — |

---

## 📁 Loyiha Strukturasi

```
budget_tracker/
├── apps/
│   ├── app_users/          # Foydalanuvchilar, JWT autentifikatsiya
│   ├── app_currencies/     # Valyutalar va CBU kurslari
│   ├── app_accounts/       # Hisob raqamlar (cash, card, bank)
│   ├── app_categories/     # Daromad/xarajat kategoriyalari
│   ├── app_transactions/   # Tranzaksiyalar va takrorlanuvchi to'lovlar
│   ├── app_reports/        # Kunlik, haftalik, oylik, yillik hisobotlar
│   └── app_dashboard/      # Umumiy moliyaviy ko'rinish
├── config/
│   └── settings.py
├── manage.py
├── requirements.txt
└── .env
```

---

## ⚙️ O'rnatish

### 1. Repositoriyani klonlash

```bash
git clone https://github.com/username/budget_tracker.git
cd budget_tracker
```

### 2. Virtual muhit yaratish

```bash
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate  # Windows
source .venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
```

### 3. Kerakli kutubxonalarni o'rnatish

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 4. `.env` faylini sozlash

`.env` faylini yarating va quyidagilarni to'ldiring:

```env
DB_NAME=budget_tracker
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=your_password
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
```

### 5. Ma'lumotlar bazasini sozlash

```bash
python manage.py migrate
```

### 6. Superuser yaratish

```bash
python manage.py createsuperuser
```

### 7. Serverni ishga tushirish

```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

---

## 🔑 Autentifikatsiya

Loyihada **JWT (JSON Web Token)** autentifikatsiyasi ishlatilgan.

- Barcha so'rovlarda `Authorization: Bearer <access_token>` header qo'shilishi kerak.
- Access token muddati: **60 daqiqa**
- Refresh token muddati: **1 kun**

---

## 📌 API Endpointlar

### 👤 Foydalanuvchilar (`/api/users/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| POST | `/api/users/register/` | Ro'yxatdan o'tish |
| POST | `/api/users/login/` | Tizimga kirish |
| POST | `/api/users/token/refresh/` | Tokenni yangilash |
| GET | `/api/users/profile/` | Profilni ko'rish |
| PATCH | `/api/users/profile/` | Profilni yangilash |
| DELETE | `/api/users/profile/` | Akkauntni deaktiv qilish |

---

### 💱 Valyutalar (`/api/currencies/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/currencies/list/` | Barcha valyutalar |
| POST | `/api/currencies/list/` | Yangi valyuta qo'shish |
| GET | `/api/currencies/detail/<pk>/` | Bitta valyuta |
| PATCH | `/api/currencies/detail/<pk>/` | Valyutani yangilash |
| DELETE | `/api/currencies/detail/<pk>/` | Valyutani o'chirish |
| POST | `/api/currencies/rates/fetch/` | CBU dan kurs olish (Admin) |

---

### 🏦 Hisoblar (`/api/accounts/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/accounts/list/` | Barcha hisoblar |
| POST | `/api/accounts/list/` | Yangi hisob yaratish |
| GET | `/api/accounts/detail/<pk>/` | Bitta hisob |
| PATCH | `/api/accounts/detail/<pk>/` | Hisobni yangilash |
| DELETE | `/api/accounts/detail/<pk>/` | Hisobni o'chirish |

---

### 🗂️ Kategoriyalar (`/api/categories/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/categories/list/` | Barcha kategoriyalar |
| POST | `/api/categories/list/` | Yangi kategoriya |
| GET | `/api/categories/detail/<pk>/` | Bitta kategoriya |
| PATCH | `/api/categories/detail/<pk>/` | Kategoriyani yangilash |
| DELETE | `/api/categories/detail/<pk>/` | Kategoriyani o'chirish |

---

### 💸 Tranzaksiyalar (`/api/transactions/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/transactions/list/` | Barcha tranzaksiyalar (filter bilan) |
| POST | `/api/transactions/list/` | Yangi tranzaksiya |
| GET | `/api/transactions/detail/<pk>/` | Bitta tranzaksiya |
| PATCH | `/api/transactions/detail/<pk>/` | Tranzaksiyani yangilash |
| DELETE | `/api/transactions/detail/<pk>/` | Tranzaksiyani o'chirish |
| GET | `/api/transactions/recurring/list/` | Takrorlanuvchi tranzaksiyalar |
| POST | `/api/transactions/recurring/list/` | Yangi takrorlanuvchi tranzaksiya |
| GET | `/api/transactions/recurring/detail/<pk>/` | Bitta takrorlanuvchi tranzaksiya |
| PATCH | `/api/transactions/recurring/detail/<pk>/` | Yangilash |
| DELETE | `/api/transactions/recurring/detail/<pk>/` | O'chirish |

#### 🔍 Filtering parametrlari

```
GET /api/transactions/list/?transaction_type=income
GET /api/transactions/list/?category=1
GET /api/transactions/list/?account=1
GET /api/transactions/list/?date_from=2026-06-01&date_to=2026-06-30
```

---

### 📊 Hisobotlar (`/api/reports/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/reports/daily/` | Kunlik hisobot |
| GET | `/api/reports/weekly/` | Haftalik hisobot |
| GET | `/api/reports/monthly/` | Oylik hisobot |
| GET | `/api/reports/yearly/` | Yillik hisobot |

#### Parametrlar

```
GET /api/reports/daily/?date=2026-06-25
GET /api/reports/monthly/?year=2026&month=06
GET /api/reports/yearly/?year=2026
```

---

### 🏠 Dashboard (`/api/dashboard/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Tavsif |
|--------|----------|--------|
| GET | `/api/dashboard/main/` | Umumiy moliyaviy ko'rinish |

**Response namunasi:**
```json
{
    "total_balance": 5000000,
    "monthly": {
        "income": 3000000,
        "expense": 1000000,
        "balance": 2000000
    },
    "transactions": [...],
    "active_recurring": 3
}
```

---

## 🔄 Takrorlanuvchi Tranzaksiyalar (Management Command)

Har kuni avtomatik ishga tushirish uchun:

```bash
python manage.py process_recurring
```

Bu command `next_run_date = bugun` bo'lgan barcha aktiv takrorlanuvchi tranzaksiyalardan avtomatik `Transaction` yaratadi va `next_run_date` ni yangilaydi.

**Takrorlanish turlari:** `daily`, `weekly`, `monthly`, `yearly`

---

## 🛡️ N+1 Muammo Yechimi

Barcha viewlarda `select_related` ishlatilgan:

```python
Transaction.objects.select_related('user', 'account', 'category', 'currency')
```

Bu 1 ta JOIN so'rovi bilan barcha bog'liq ma'lumotlarni olib keladi.

